text: Stefan Müller (born 9 November 1988 in Karlsruhe) is a German footballer who plays for KSV Hessen Kassel. Müller made his debut for Karlsruher SC on 3 April 2010, in a 1–1 away draw against 1. FC Union Berlin, after coming off the bench to replace Anton Fink in the 89th minute. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Karlsruhe Category:German footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:2.
